{"tid":1475871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"818請用完全和理非遊行做宣傳！！！","createTime":"2019-08-15T15:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:14:31.000Z","uid":77755,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"0fac1cf12cc930b64f3458e04ed118ce9b7601ea","tid":1475871,"uid":77755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"大家都認同今次由民陣吹雞遊行係為左曬馬 顯示民意 顯示香港人仲係落力爭取緊五大訴求 <br />\n但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依家有個好大既問題係警方對遊行發左反對通知書</span></span><br />\n平時出慣黎既手足梗係唔擔心啦 照行就照行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但重點係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好多和理非真係完全配合警方指示 警方出左反對通知書就唔敢出黎</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非特性就係唔(敢)做踩界犯法既事</span></span><br />\n如果依家用平時方法宣傳 雖然佢地唔會割勇武 但以往績黎睇 佢地多數會覺得出黎一定食煙而驚咗<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地依家應該用全和理非宣傳鼓勵佢地出黎</span></span></strong><br />\n要明白 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對和理非黎講 反抗反對通知書 係一個好大既心理關口 因為可能會犯法喎！！</span></span> <br />\n如果今次有100萬人肯對抗反對通知書而出黎  唔通警察記者會譴責100萬人參與非法集結咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而如果和理非第1次做左「犯法」既事 將會打破到佢地對於「犯法事不能做」既心理關口 <br />\n直接幫助到佢地接受示威者使用適當既武力對抗暴政<br />\n我認為效果絕對不亞於616 200萬人參與既<span style=\"color: green;\">合法</span>示威！<br />\n<br />\n但重申 人不犯狗 狗都有機會犯人 <br />\nGear要帶 用黎自保之用<br />\n如果狗真係放tear gas既話 勇武幫到和理非手足 亦係加分位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望勇武手足明白 唔係話你地無用 知道你地能屈能伸 一定可以全力配合 <br />\n起碼呢幾日唔好不停講自己準備咩榴彈炮 818招呼啲狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n818 全民和理非遊行 無懼警方白色恐怖 直接幫和理非升級做勇武 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5102ae6f3110ac2cdeebf1d85a071da101d76f","tid":1475871,"uid":77755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:28:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e20a59740bc0dc60b537b6a2103034ef3ae7b62","tid":1475871,"uid":77755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:28:52.000Z","msg":"推到有人回"},{"pid":"91e0abd572d7a3f955e1535b51c2bad027df91bf","tid":1475871,"uid":77755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:29:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4cde886aa0bcb881ed3e7482de265f5c804307","tid":1475871,"uid":77755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:29:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f81b388b74d4e00ef47096385a0c05ca98487ece","tid":1475871,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:29:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0d0eafd93931d8cdd118f61622cabd422699545d","tid":1475871,"uid":77755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:29:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"571d2a21fdb24ee748f1d36e7be7c0a15daa2b8c","tid":1475871,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LhC4hEz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLhC4hEz.jpg&h=dee9093d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hmjm4jA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhmjm4jA.jpg&h=b7a22bba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YF0dVrf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYF0dVrf.jpg&h=4974a9ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fc9f280dc260646