ets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各有各做!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727a224f91c41a090c372890f9ca648a5270d390","tid":1475871,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:32:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38dd6890ff476c1b197594ec71480211ab06ec62","tid":1475871,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:32:24.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"007aca80dcc4c8ebcea36d13328f0afc48954855","tid":1475871,"uid":59341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:32:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd04bdc6d7a23cdbdf34fca82756f57d367e7ac9","tid":1475871,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:32:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"833152891e33d3a6f9536b7746d116d47fcb6d49","tid":1475871,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f13b84150cc86fc151d03d099440c1ba555446","tid":1475871,"uid":194399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:32:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d31fcdf9bf33fefe304a3663d32084eb48e57a4a","tid":1475871,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家就係和理非同冷靜既時候<br />\n拖落去中共必輸<br />\n所以佢一定會做好多手段激化沖突<br />\n大家小心!!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"55fd12a105310d9e17d4dcafb89e2afa7c32dcd4","tid":1475871,"uid":66049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:33:42.000Z","msg":"其實仲需要一班真係想和平遊行完就走嘅人<br />\n特別有小朋友、中產、八十後<br />\n起碼佢地肯出嚟<br />\n多過71 50萬"},{"pid":"e37bfb27f0959b70f41b9a7e05f1172b24277361","tid":1475871,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:33:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">NOW OR NEVER</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dYUik2W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdYUik2W.jpg&h=b7b2e1de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hrs0znW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHrs0znW.png&h=d1fc316e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xqMkznX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxqMkznX.jpg&h=c5dabcdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hvEPWh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hvEPWh.jpg&h=f7d69869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEYbF2X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEYbF2X.jpg&h=f6523fdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9TAab9D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9TAab9D.jpg&h=59c68e7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66a66dac49046aa1ee8d85743e554cd6d59ae323","tid":1475871,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"818 和理優 日 行坐企，<br />\n所有 其他行為&nbsp; 入晒 警 25 仔數"},{"pid":"3f240fe5cb2cab115875cc1f6ef9c988c43f51f6","tid":1475871,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:35:01.000Z","msg":"818係要show團結，唔行就坐爆維園，唔夠坐就坐爆港島<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475691\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475691</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"882d94e92076d868420af3973dbed85ade3bdf3c","tid":1475871,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:36:27.000Z","msg":"818 根本唔需要「勇武」行為<br />\n<br />\n1) 狗政府唔撚出批文, 就係因為以次次遊行都有衝突為由, 所以818 一定事後要無衝突, 已經可以狠狠地打鳩狗政府一巴 。<br />\n<br />\n2) 818 出嚟既人數應該唔會少 , 點都有幾十萬, 有老有嫩 (希望612 有人數) , 衝突係會令依班老嫩嚇驚。<br />\n<br />\n3) 依家個個星期都有衝突, 818 係最好機會轉一次玩法, 睇下完全無衝突之下, 政府仲有咩藉口好屌<br />\n<br />\n4) 818 一定要有共識, 唔起衝突, 69 , 612 嗰班小市民先會放心再行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n5) 如果有左唔衝突既共識 , 但有人出嚟「製造」混亂, 就可以證明咩人專登搞亂<br />\n<br />\n6) 極需要一次完美既和平示威去做國際文宣"},{"pid":"4ebde8b4832309eff7c7b5db07776e1c99ef7bcc","tid":1475871,"uid":77755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:39:22.000Z","msg":"比負評既手足出黎講下!"},{"pid":"4aab4d0938cc397b4c56e4fef2b1c58c96e75732","tid":1475871,"uid":77755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:40:35.000Z","msg":"本身811發生左太多不公既事 絕對可以煲大佢 <br />\n只差一步就係點樣令到啲人無懼反對通知書企出黎!"},{"pid":"f304a4b8e72e73ac3b8900acb9a9d6cc17852818","tid":1475871,"uid":77755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:41:45.000Z","msg":"請文宣盡量煲大811既事!<br />\n只差一步就係點樣令到啲人無懼反對通知書企出黎!"},{"pid":"f9a4b9fa94e20e6da61eeaa8be0b7bffbbe3c8ad","tid":1475871,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:42:05.000Z","msg":"當上次話和理優<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289bd3a39e681d3c0b7d33bc3ef7a06ff579afde","tid":1475871,"uid":77755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71aa66989f54deae4bf51e5443faf0d1c4905eb4","tid":1475871,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d25f75f83e47287df3a34a757834e9cc2bd7cb","tid":1475871,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,